\b Benchmark Details\

\b0\i \

\i0 The DSP sine ROM is used as the wavetable for all oscillators above.  All vibrato is done on the DSP.  The amount of synthesis that can be done in real time also depends on how rapidly wave tables are changing and other details of musical context.  Changing the constitution of the orchestra during a performance can lead to somewhat smaller numbers due to DSP memory fragmentation.\

